11:05.720 --> 11:09.140
So it's better for Ubuntu Mate, it's better for the Unity remix as well.

11:09.140 --> 11:15.660
All this has been going down on the Ubuntu community hub, and one name popped up, Martin

11:15.660 --> 11:16.660
