12:50.780 --> 12:54.660
maybe a little bit, and the Wayland stuff, of course.

12:54.660 --> 12:58.940
But if there's people working on it, then why not let it live alongside Chrome?

12:58.940 --> 13:04.300
Yeah, and I also think there's a place for Unity with an updated theme.

